summary: I am currently working as a Senior Business Intelligence Consultant for Neudesic.Current - Boyd Gaming Customer Card Near Real-Time SolutionSSIS project to import Customer information from one system to another at or Near Real Time.Using Stored Procedure, User Defined Table Type, and Table Variables to populate tables through a C# Script Task in an SSIS package.Sally Beauty Data-warehouse migration to SQL Server 2016. Refactor system to run under current SQL Server 2016 features and add new architecture to business needs. Hess Oil Data-mart , Architect and Developer on a 3 month Data-mart project. Creation using SSIS and SQL Server 2014 on AWS VM. Full ETL implementation using framework and processing over 3000 csv's. Assurant properties Enterprise Data warehouse implementation. Using SSIS and SSAS , provided an end to end Data warehouse solution. Fact and Dimension modeling and Architecture of full ETL solution. CEC Entertainment INC project to provide Integration between new vendors through SSIS and C# applications running as services. As a Sogeti consultant I worked at Arizona Department of Education as a Senior SSIS developer. Creating new processes to integrate data into their online System for Teacher Assessments. Maintain ADE's system on a SQL Server 2012 platform using SSIS project deployment. Worked as a SQL DBA for Godaddy.com, duties include support of the E commerce system and database maintenance. Fix old and create new business processes in stored procedures. Worked in an agile/scrum environment.  Worked at Aetna as a Senior Application Specialists. I work mainly as a SQL Server Developer maintaining an RDBMS system that is continually growing. Providing production support and new improvements to the system. I am also converting DTS to SSIS packages, maintaining an SSRS instance and also providing new enhancements to the system.For Informz a SaaS company, I provided Email Marketing solutions via SQL Server.
